}

### 5. Verify Token (Copy token from login response)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Get All Accounts
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/accounts

### 7. Update Account
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/accounts/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "john_updated",
  "email": "john_updated@example.com",
  "password": "newpassword123",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

### 8. Delete Account
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/accounts/1
